commit.message: No need to build Python 3.7 anymore
Update deployment of source code from Python 3.11 manylinux

fix(setup): `numpy` included in `setup_requires` (#74)

since numpy is already included in setup_requires, https://github.com/htseq/htseq/commit/061a963bba6a3a58decaa61d64cd26d3246ad740 , the `import numpy` etc should not be necessary; however, it can break package managers when numpy happens to not be installed in sequence before htseq
Signed-off-by: Cameron Smith <cameron.ray.smith@gmail.com>
